;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl851&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid rgb(191, 191, 191); white-space: nowrap; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;DATOS OPER. ORIGINAL&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl853&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid rgb(191, 191, 191); white-space: nowrap; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;27&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl851&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid rgb(191, 191, 191); white-space: nowrap; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Alfanumerico&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl851&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid rgb(191, 191, 191); white-space: nowrap; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Opcional&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;534&quot; class=&quot;xl854&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-a