        <mxCell id="EAzvslMnZkLetL4-adom-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;DIAGRAMA DE FLUJO (DESCRIPCIÓN NARRATIVA)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__hr&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; width: 715px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Inicio del proceso&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• El proceso inicia cuando el sistema recibe una solicitud de “transferencia de canales internos”.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Paso 1: Identificar tipo de casuística&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• El sistema lee el tipo de operación solicitada.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Se evalúa si la casuística es:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ul&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: circle;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Aplicación de abono a crédito&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ul&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: circle;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Cargo a débito&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ul&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: circle;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Cargo a crédito&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ul&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: circle;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Pago (escenario dependiente de PLA)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ul&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: circle;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Anulación (pendiente de validación por PLA)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Paso 2: Validación funcional&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• El sistema valida si la casuística está habilitada y confirmada.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Si la casuística no ha sido confirmada (por ejemplo, un escenario pendiente que Juan debe confirmar), el flujo se detiene y se regresa una notificación de “caso no autorizado”.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Paso 3: Obtener información del flujo&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Si la casuística es válida, el sistema consulta la capa de integración y los destinos correspondientes.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• La capa de integración determina el sistema destino según la casuística.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Paso 4: Procesar la operación&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Para abono a crédito: se genera la instrucción de abono y se envía al sistema destino.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Para cargo a débito: se genera la instrucción de cargo y se envía.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Para cargo a crédito: se genera el cargo hacia el sistema perteneciente a “Plata”.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Para pagos: se solicita información a PLA para obtener parámetros del pago y procesarlo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Para anulaciones: se solicita a PLA validar el proceso y ejecutar la anulación.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Paso 5: Recepción de respuesta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• El sistema destino responde si la operación fue exitosa o rechazada.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Paso 6: Generar resultado&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Si la respuesta es exitosa, se registra el movimiento y se devuelve confirmación.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alte