rride: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Actor principal&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Sistema origen o canal que envía la solicitud&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;(por ejemplo: un módulo interno que ejecuta los movimientos)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; 